 constant times the Fourier transform of the fourth-order correlation
-function, $$\phi(\tau) = \langle E^2(t)E^2(t + \tau) \rangle$$ at the
+function,
+$$
+\phi(\tau) = \langle E^2(t)E^2(t + \tau) \rangle \tag{1}
+$$
+at the
