Edited `content/papers/quantum.beats.md` with minimal structural QA changes only.

Summary of changes:
- Added visible KaTeX equation numbering tags `\tag{1}` through `\tag{8}` to the existing display equations, without changing any equation content.
- Ensured in-text references to equation `(5)` are now resolvable to a visible numbered display equation.
- Inserted missing blank-line paragraph breaks at clear paragraph boundaries (including before `## References and Notes` and around the long EPR/cavity transition section).
- Kept paper meaning/content unchanged; no figure handling changes; no abstract duplication found to remove.
